snippet.title: LOCK-ON (Arcade, Tatsumi/Data East, 1986) 720p HD 60fps
snippet.description:
Just a quick capture from a relatively obscure '80s arcade game. My friend and I used to play this a lot at the Family Fun Center in Fountain Valley, CA. Pretty good effects for a game that's close to 30 years old now!
